{"tid":2044180,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！！Twitter有多國語言嘅文宣！","createTime":"2020-05-31T02:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T08:46:16.000Z","uid":239825,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc5712e3ebd91f2994be4358395f1bc64bf75ad0","tid":2044180,"uid":239825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"Twitter要人打國際線！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日見到IAD出咗多國語言嘅文宣係twitter <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwygXR9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwygXR9.png&h=7b157000&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLGKniQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLGKniQ.png&h=8b6a894c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見到美日法德文呢啲當然唔少得 但係仲有例如芬蘭文呢啲版本都有 我哋要人一齊幫手傳開去比多啲人睇到份文宣！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想攬炒就係要突破同溫層 搵多啲國家一齊嚟幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />If we burn you burn with us!</span></span>"},{"pid":"94d50bbe43f57de5c033e4944dc8e4cec60f25c3","tid":2044180,"uid":239825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed3a4ba0a2d51e6cb548222fa763db840870458e","tid":2044180,"uid":239825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:00:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab44d61a9ddec142f906100c9d0efc481102cf9","tid":2044180,"uid":239825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:32:03.